## My Contributions

My main contributions focused on improving reliability, maintainability, and asset-loading behavior in the game.

### Key Fixes

- Improved `find_game_file()` so the game can locate files across multiple possible folder layouts.
- Updated `clean_sprite_name()` to correctly detect `double_jump` before `jump`.
- Added logic for handling different asset naming patterns.
- Improved sprite animation key normalization.
- Added safer file and folder lookup behavior.
- Helped prevent missing assets from crashing the game.
- Improved compatibility when the game file is placed in different project directories.

